com.safenetinc.luna.attributes

Class LunaPkcs11Attributes

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.safenetinc.luna.attributes.LunaPkcs11Attributes

  • public class LunaPkcs11Attributes
extends java.lang.Object
    This class stores PKCS11 attribute values that can be used to control the attribute values that are specified at the native layer for key generation.
    See Also:
    LunaPkcs11AttributesConfig, LunaPkcs11AttributesParameterSpec
